**SPADA:**  
Tell me what you need.

**ZAZIO (after a pause):**  
Not money. Not thanks. Just let us finish the job. Don’t let the Senate cancel the next round. Let us go to the slums too—not just the homes that pay.

**SPADA:**  
You have my word. And may God grant you strength.

**ZAZIO (quietly):**  
We burn everything except hope.

[[Next|The End]]


