''4 persons are in the chamber''

CARDINAL-LEGATE BERNARDINO SPADA, stern in scarlet robes, fingers steepled as if in prayer—or suppression.

DR. BARTOLOMEO AMBROSINI, physician, clutching notes that reek of vinegar.

SENATOR OTTAVIO DI ANTONIO, silk sleeves rustling like dried leaves, face a mask of patrician calm.

